
# Splunk Queries

## View Imported Log

```spl
source="portscan.log"
```

---

## Count Captured Packets

```spl
source="portscan.log"
| stats count
```

---

## Search SYN Packets

```spl
source="portscan.log" "Flags [S]"
```

---

## Search Destination Port

```spl
source="portscan.log" "22"
```

---

## Dashboard Query

```spl
source="portscan.log"
| stats count AS "Captured Packets"
```
